<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>보증서를 찾을 수 없습니다 | ARK PROJECT</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@600&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    * { box-sizing:border-box; margin:0; padding:0; }
    body { font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif; background:linear-gradient(160deg,#1A3620,#0E1F12); color:#FBF8F0; min-height:100vh; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; padding:24px; text-align:center; }
    .logo { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; color:#D4AF37; letter-spacing:3px; font-size:16px; margin-bottom:18px; }
    h1 { font-size:20px; font-weight:500; margin-bottom:10px; }
    p { font-size:14px; color:#E8D9A0; opacity:0.85; line-height:1.7; }
    code { color:#D4AF37; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div>
    <div class="logo">ARK PROJECT · BY JIYANG</div>
    <h1>보증서를 찾을 수 없습니다</h1>
    <p>고유번호 <code><%= id %></code> 에 해당하는 보증서가 존재하지 않습니다.<br/>번호를 다시 확인해 주시거나 지양하월시아로 문의해 주세요.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
